snippet.title: Fatal Frame Xbox Longplay
snippet.description:
Also known as Fatal Frame: Special Edition in Japan or Project Zero in Europe
This version of Fatal Frame has more unlockables, and an extra difficulty that has more ghosts and a new ending, the ending is kind of like the nightmare ending but has it cut shorter than the other endings and has a slideshow play during the credits
I don't show the extra difficulties but I do show their endings and the Fatal difficulty that is Xbox exclusive has one extra ghost fight that I show before it's unique ending.
This version also changes a lot of the lighting in many areas to make it easier to see
